{"tid":224004,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"聽人老點，買部Switch同女朋友玩，而家嬲咗我","createTime":"2017-04-30T16:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T01:40:06.000Z","uid":78971,"like":8,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c0748cc4857a12ca2092bd1bd052cb3809fed31","tid":224004,"uid":78971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:53:23.000Z","msg":"同佢玩孖車<br />\n玩完一局playback啲畫面<br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一個畫面係佢想撞人撞到自己停曬咁濟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：呢個模式係鬥快架，玩碰碰車咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算係碰碰車，你又撞唔到人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我知！唔撞又點過佢呀<br />\n<br />\n第二個畫面係影到佢揸得好慢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：嘩你安全駕駛架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家叫你考牌咩，考牌都揸得快過你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：......<br />\n<br />\n第三個畫面係我喺後面掉紅龜殼中咗佢之後過佢，個角色做咗個「Yes」嘅動作<br />\n佢就放低手掣走咗<br />\n<br />\n問題嚟喇<br />\n想問下Switch仲有咩雙打game好玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好係協力架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6827f5d4560ae3a05388b8481bbcecc2493f246","tid":224004,"uid":6464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:54:03.000Z","msg":"12好好玩"},{"pid":"3cf9eddb22e75d3b5d5c0f7d4148f929b588da3a","tid":224004,"uid":68309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:55:30.000Z","msg":"Bomberman 有協力"},{"pid":"6afc31f192223a14074b7496e84d5289216a7fff","tid":224004,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20